displayName: City of the Forest, Wald - Item Shop

parameters: Clea: I went to see the request form.

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: That would be a great help! I
want you to go to the Kasaro Bathhouse in my place.
Clea: I am greatly indebted to Mr. Kasaro.

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: I'm grateful to the goddess
Actina! What I want you to transport is high-quality
firewood for heating the bathwater.
Priestess Sophia: Hic, beer isn't bad at all!

Priestess Sophia: Oh my...! Have you injured your leg by
any chance?
Clea: Sophia-san, we're in front of the client.

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: Ahaha, it's embarrassing, but
it happened while I was cutting.

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: Tell the manager of the
Kasaro Bathhouse that I will go there next time to fix it
immediately.

Priestess Sophia: Understood, I will pray for your injury
to heal as soon as possible!

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: I don't worship the goddess
Imiserinos, but ahaha, it's not a bad thing to have a
beautiful woman pray for you.

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: It's the best that you
especially love beer.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Torch Firewood Craftsman: Sorry, but I can't make it to the
Kasaro Bathhouse with these legs you asked for.

Torch the Firewood Craftsman: I'm glad you're safe. The
Kasaro Bathhouse is our most valued customer, after all.
